  <title>Zoom in and zoom out</title>

  <p>To increase <app>Terminal</app> text size:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Select <guiseq><gui style="menu">View</gui>
      <gui style="menuitem">Zoom In</gui></guiseq> or press
      <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>+</key></keyseq>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>To decrease <app>Terminal</app> text size:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Select <guiseq><gui style="menu">View</gui>
      <gui style="menuitem">Zoom Out</gui></guiseq> or press
      <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>-</key></keyseq>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>To restore <app>Terminal</app> text to default size:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Select <guiseq><gui style="menu">View</gui> <gui
      style="menuitem">Normal Size</gui></guiseq> or press
      <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>0</key></keyseq>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

